/><br />\n如果ching 有時間<br />\n不妨分享下你覺得音樂點為之「美」<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想聽下大家點樣衡量音樂好唔好聽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:57:39.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n<br />\n唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個話題好broad 而且好個人好潛意識<br />\n而且你如果要問我咩top10 list我應該都比唔到你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我淨係簡單咁講下點解我鍾意l&rsquo;isle joyeuse 而唔鍾意clair de lune <br />\n主要個分別係一個比較動態 一個比較靜態<br />\n而係l&rsquo;isle joyeuse入邊 你可以明題感受到佢個音樂形態(正確翻譯應該係morphology)<br />\n你唔使特登去問果啲係咩音 而係去感受譜上面既線條<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qP5jixf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqP5jixf.png&h=1835b167&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JYGFNqB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJYGFNqB.png&h=43a704f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你可以見到（or聽到）佢豐富既律動 同鮮明既音樂形態<br />\n<br />\n相對 clair de lune 就比較靜態 律動隔好遠 而且感受唔到佢有咩音樂形態（主要係頭兩版 佢中間都偏正常）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKJpuHR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKJpuHR.png&h=c4842e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（唔知可以點畫線...）佢係有旋律 但係太鬆散 強度太弱form唔到 一種音樂形態 你留意翻l&rsquo;isle joyeuse佢個impulse 同形態係同時發生既 而clair de lune佢chord出現係98既正拍上 但係作用純粹就係比係感受佢旋律個節拍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Um6H7L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Um6H7L.png&h=b91369e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再加埋堆chord 本身太協和 冇緊張度 就令成個開頭太blend 太鬆 <br />\n於是 clair de lune係我耳中 聽更加似只係一堆chord (9/11/13? 冇睇）"},{"pid":"c0c756cb9dcfa82d262181de30bee418cfbf0923","tid":2425770,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T20:06:32.000Z","msg":"應該係話我主要就聽到一堆旋律既parallel 3rd<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f385e017ee241cd241ba8f749be07affaee6dd9","tid":2425770,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1x1KEphfpDE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.